哈 她还爱读书
Ah she reads.

802
01:07:24,522 --> 01:07:29,214
Bronte  Jane Austen 和Sophocles (均为著名作家)
Bronte, Jane Austen and Sophocles.

803
01:07:29,258 --> 01:07:30,230
请进
Coming.

804
