I was blind with anger and grief.

889
01:12:46,942 --> 01:12:50,934
我甚至想不起我是怎么到那儿去的
I have no recollection of even how I got there.

890
01:12:53,310 --> 01:12:56,539
我只知道有一天我发现我自己
I only know that I found myself one day

891
01:12:58,324 --> 01:13:02,016
